data.description: OPEN HOUSE Saturday 1-6-2024 from 12pm-2pm. This beautiful 3-bedroom 2 bath home with a study is located in highly sought after Villages of Woodland Springs and award-winning Keller ISD. Home features New Paint, New countertops, New backsplash, New landscaping and an open floor plan. Kitchen features New sink, quartz countertops, an island with a walk-in pantry and more. Master suite offers double vanity, separate tub & shower and large walk-in closet. Backyard features a covered patio with plenty of room for entertaining family and friends. Close to dining, shopping, schools and major highways. Come see today before it's too late.
